-- entry: ETestDev执行用例入口函数 
-- @vars: 输入参数, @option: 自定义选项
function entry(vars, option)
	print('hello')
    verify(true, 'verify true')
    verify(false, 'verify false')
    log.check('check true', true)
    log.check('check false', false)
    for i=1, 1000 do
        record.x = i
        delay(1)
    end
    print('hello2')
    delay(1)
    log.info('log info')
    log.warn('log warn')
    log.error('log error')

    for i=1, 1000 do
        record.x = i*10
        delay(1)
    end
    
    assert(true, 'assert true')
	assert(false, 'assert fail')
    exit()
end

content.script:
function fn_test(var) 
    print("var =", var)
    print("test run begin")
    delay(1)
    print("test run end")
end

function entry(vars, option)
    -- 订阅事件 test_event
    async.on("test_event", fn_test)     
    delay(1000)

    -- 触发事件
    async.emit("test_event", 123)
    async.emit("test_event", 456)
    print("test_event emited")
    delay(1000)

    -- 关闭订阅
    async.off("test_event")
    exit()
end
